Package tools.data.collection.rb_tree

Class LinkedRBKey<D extends LinkedRBKey<D>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tools.data.collection.rb_tree.LinkedRBKey<D>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<D>
    public abstract class LinkedRBKey<D extends LinkedRBKey<D>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<D>
    This key class is used for the LinkedRBTree data structure. The user of this data structure should extends this class.

    When searching through the tree, one can use all function of this class in O(1) time.
    See Also:
    LinkedRBNode, LinkedRBTree
